Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨的伊奧利亞·肖漢博格的亡靈們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我亞里桑德羅·科納
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來把你們超度到新世界去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始驅逐目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 瞄準莢倉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣好的話 能炸了那對鉗子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 毫髮無傷麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑那種程度就想對抗Alva Torre
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑之至
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 告訴我機師們的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N…Nadleeh損壞嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞…全無應答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 機體損傷多處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與敵方兩架MS交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長翅膀的在衛星群的什麼地方躲起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種機體狀況逃不了多遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了麼 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回裡面去 阿雷路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒你這生死線上什麼都做不到的傢伙什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要吸乾其他生者的血也會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 還沒聽到世界的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這場戰鬥的意義也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞭解到那些之前 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於有那種意思了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去給那女人看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超兵」的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直線攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避給你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合軸線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出腳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並同時攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:03:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒功夫像以前那樣慢悠悠的!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 阿雷路亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那武器是和Throne一樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 連接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN兵裝什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獠牙!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力場展開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈無虛發
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真能躲開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝上去了啊 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是白癡的老一套
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃這招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 區區一架Gundam就把我的Alva Torre…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 我明明是完美的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不清楚啊 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是完美的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然通過腦量子波得到了非同一般的反應能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你的思想卻達不到那種速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是像動物一樣遵照本能行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此能看透你的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應和思想融合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是超兵應有的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個光輝是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的那個麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼 不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續戰鬥 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐如果不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就變成獨自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪…瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞 回答 拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是擁有原始太陽爐的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半吊子的機師就讓我這樣難堪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你這傢伙吧 扭曲了伊奧利亞的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃還在進行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是主角換成我了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 主角就是我 亞里桑德羅·科納
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有何企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞與再生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過天行者的武力介入 世界被毀滅 並以統一的姿態開始再生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 我要把這個世界染上我的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要支配一切麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是引導世界踏上正途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個新世界裡 沒有你存在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你轟殺至渣  Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾啊 伊奧利亞·肖漢博格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統一世界 引導人類進入新時代的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我這個現在還活著的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞的系統麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 扭曲世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你就是元兇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的新生已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還要繼續破壞下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 你知道為什麼Exia裝備了實體劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了與GN力場對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因為計劃中也包括了與Gundam進行的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真到了那時 你就是我們最後的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一個只會戰鬥的破壞者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要戰鬥  為了打倒那些引起紛爭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了擊碎這個世界的扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用武力來根絕戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力場被…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡本斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞里桑德羅 科納
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個不錯的小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是伊奧利亞·肖漢博格的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是按我的計劃進行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡本斯 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界統一的未來就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 毀了科納家族的夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這麼說的話 還是你自己太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡本斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flag 擬造太陽爐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想與你相會 想與你相會阿 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束劍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍華德和達裡爾的仇 由我來為他們報
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這台GN驅動器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有通信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那個時候的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你我之前是被命運的紅線連在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是戰鬥的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:15:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以壓倒性的性能 奪走了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺 就是愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是超越了愛之後 就變成了憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像過於執著的信仰也引發了內戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你明白 又為什麼要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問軍人為什麼而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為Gundam的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界什麼的怎麼樣都沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己本身就是世界的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這就是世界的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了 你只是執著於自我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:16:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的扭曲 就由我來斬斷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能說阿 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍華德 達裡爾 你們的仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在這裡結束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃還在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把太陽爐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh放出了GN驅動器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣終於能來到你的身邊 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 索瑪·皮瑞斯居然是瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道了嗎 哈雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道了的話 你就無法戰鬥了 只有死路一條
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正是玩笑 我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷魯亞 難道說 怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露 當你在讀這封信的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不存於這世上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過武力來根絕戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者組織告訴了只會一味戰鬥的我 戰鬥的意義所在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像當初的Gundam那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直渴求著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界為什麼會如此扭曲 這扭曲又從何而來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人為什麼會抱有無意識的惡意 卻又意識不到這股惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有那些攪亂人生的事物存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼人們要支配他人 被他人支配
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要互相傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 人們又為什麼如此想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 一直追尋著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只要能與你相見 就一定能獲得解答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以不同的方式 追尋著同樣的事物的你一定能回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們能共同前進的道路 這一答案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直追尋著 和Gundam一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Gundam一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲 好久沒給你寫信了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從你沒有回信開始 已經過了兩年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我有件事無論如何想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從今年開始將在宇宙工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有許多令人悲傷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我實現了這一小小的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想要實現另一個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著你 露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是GN粒子的光嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裡的機體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是聯邦的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子的顏色不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那光是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:21:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正值國際聯合改名為地球聯邦一週年之際
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經全聯邦328個成員國的贊同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此宣佈將各國的軍隊解體 組建一元化的地球聯邦維和部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當所有國家的軍隊不復存在 我們維和部隊成為世界唯一軍隊之時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界將獲得真正的統一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將以此為道標 穩步前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 世界算是改變了吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道 你對現在的世界不滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有所期待 對世界的改變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了 革新 人類的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞您大駕了 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一架已經出產了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在做實戰準備的測試
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的機體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按計劃將依次出產
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.49,0:22:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話能讓我觀摩一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一代的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是0 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.12,0:23:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一台搭載太陽爐運作的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已將卸下的太陽爐組裝上了機體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算這個也不匹配
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.67,0:23:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用Exia的太陽爐也不知能否順利運作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變世界的機體 00 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------
