Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:47.58,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}my wishes over their airspace
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:57.09,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}無数の波を超え　明日へ立ち向かうあなたを　守りたまえ
